<I as data::ElementIterator<N, E>>::I: impl<N, E, I: ?Sized> ElementIterator<N, E> for I where I: Iterator<Item = Element<N, E>> {}

<I as iter_utils::IterUtilsExt>::I: impl<I> IterUtilsExt for I where I: Iterator {}
<M as algo::Measure>::M: impl<M> Measure for M where M: Debug + PartialOrd + Add<M, Output = M> + Default + Clone {}
<N as graphmap::NodeTrait>::N: impl<N> NodeTrait for N where N: Copy + Ord + Hash {}
csr::EdgeReference: impl<'a, E, Ty, Ix: Copy> Copy for EdgeReference<'a, E, Ty, Ix> {}

}
